ersities., ',null,'Priority to applicants eligible for free or reduced price lunch for 73% of seats',null,'Basketball, Outdoor Track, Soccer, Table Tennis, Wrestling','Basketball, Cross Country, Flag Football, Rugby, Soccer, Softball, Table Tennis, Volleyball','10th Grade Seats Available,Diversity in Admissions,Early College');
